author: johnh
msg: Makes HttpResponseBuilder extend MutableContent. The underlying semantics of the class remain the same -- two new mutation APIs are added as well. By default, HTML parsing is not supported (ie. with new HttpResponseBuilder().getDocument()), which is status quo.
This change is a step toward updating the HTTP object rewriter interface with HttpResponseBuilder as mutation object.
